  "pedagogy": "Vowels (3/4): closed o (โ◌ะ/โ◌) vs open o (เ◌าะ/◌อ), and oe (เ◌อะ/เ◌อ). Concept: Thai distinguishes two o qualities; อ as a vowel letter.",
